        "from prophet import Prophet\n",
        "from prophet.plot import plot_plotly, plot_components_plotly\n",
        "model = Prophet()\n",
        "model.fit(forecast_data)\n",
        "forecasts = model.make_future_dataframe(periods=365)\n",
        "predictions = model.predict(forecasts)\n",
        "plot_plotly(model, predictions)"

        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "from statsmodels.tsa.arima.model import ARIMA\n",
        "\n",
        "# Load the dataset\n",
        "weather_data = pd.read_csv(\"/content/Arima Code Data.csv\", parse_dates=[\"date\"], index_col=\"date\", dayfirst=True)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Fit the ARIMA model\n",
        "model = ARIMA(weather_data[\"meantemp\"], order=(1, 1, 1))\n",
        "model_fit = model.fit()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Define the forecast start and end dates\n",
        "forecast_start_date = weather_data.index[-1]\n",
        "forecast_end_date = forecast_start_date + pd.DateOffset(days=14)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Fit the ARIMA model\n",
        "model = ARIMA(weather_data[\"meantemp\"], order=(3, 3, 3))\n",
        "model_fit = model.fit()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Make predictions for the next 15 days\n",
        "forecast = model_fit.forecast(steps=7)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Print the forecasted values\n",
        "print(\"Temperature forecast for the next 7 days:\")\n",
        "print(forecast)\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "# Repeat for humidity and windspeed\n",
        "model = ARIMA(weather_data[\"humidity\"], order=(2, 2, 5))\n",
        "model_fit = model.fit()\n",
        "forecast = model_fit.forecast(steps=7)\n",
        "print(\"Humidity forecast for the next 7 days:\")\n",
        "print(forecast)\n",
        "\n",
        "model = ARIMA(weather_data[\"wind_speed\"], order=(2, 1, 2))\n",
        "model_fit = model.fit()\n",
        "forecast = model_fit.forecast(steps=7)\n",
        "print(\"Windspeed forecast for the next 7 days:\")\n",
        "print(forecast)\n",
        "\n"
      ],
